caption.p: Impact of carvacrol, thymol, and their combination on the viability of the HL60 myeloid leukemic cells. Flow cytometric analysis of cell death with Annexin V-FITC/PI double staining after 24 h and 48 h treatment with different concentrations of carvacrol and thymol (individually or in combination). Data represent the mean Â± SEM of three independent experiments relative to vehicle. The levels of statistical significance were set at p < 0.01 (**) p < 0.001 (***).
